nt|Here is a useful tip: It is sometimes good strategy at IMP scoring to overbid on complex distributional hands. Sometimes you will get too high and go down in game, but if there is a game in the cards you will at least be able to find the best trump suit more often if you bid out your hand as naturally as possible. |
